The TM200 ProgressiveTraction introduces VF technology to specialized crops like vineyards and orchards, delivering precision, stability, and soil protection. Its low-pressure operation minimizes compaction while boosting traction and comfort. Designed for versatility, it combines advanced tread engineering and premium materials for durable performance with reduced environmental impact
